ent-RMCSynthResetKey = We-Yu synthetic reset key
    .desc = This device can fix major glitches or programming errors of synthetic units, as well as being able to restart a synthetic that has suffered critical failure. It must be recharged after use.

ent-RMCSynthResetKeyHyperdyne = Hyperdyne synthetic reset key
    .desc = A Hyperdyne-pattern reset key for rebooting synthetic units after critical failure. It must be recharged after use.

ent-RMCSynthResetKeyHyperdyneSMART = SMART Hyperdyne synthetic reset key
    .desc = A Hyperdyne-pattern reset key with a microfunction AI, allowing anyone to operate it. It must be recharged after use.

ent-RMCSynthResetKeyMakeshift = makeshift synthetic sparker
    .desc = A crude synthetic reboot device assembled from scavenged sparking electronics. It must be recharged after use.

ent-RMCSynthResetKeyNovaris = Novaris synthetic reset key
    .desc = An independent Novaris design, based on a previous collaboration with Weyland-Yutani. This device can fix major glitches or programming errors of synthetic units, as well as being able to restart a synthetic that has suffered critical failure. It must be recharged after use.

ent-RMCSynthResetKeyNovarisSMART = SMART Novaris synthetic reset key
    .desc = An independent Novaris design, based on a previous collaboration with Weyland-Yutani. This device can fix major glitches or programming errors of synthetic units, as well as being able to restart a synthetic that has suffered critical failure. It must be recharged after use. This one has a micro-function AI and can be operated by anyone.

ent-RMCSynthResetKeySMART = SMART We-Yu synthetic reset key
    .desc = This device can fix major glitches or programming errors of synthetic units, as well as being able to restart a synthetic that has suffered critical failure. It must be recharged after use. This one has a microfunction AI and can be operated by anyone.

ent-RMCSynthResetKeySeegson = Seegson Working Joe reboot key
    .desc = A rugged reboot key designed for Seegson Working Joe synthetic units. It must be recharged after use.
